testsuite.name: com.tim.one.service.BreakevenServiceIntegrationSpec

testcase.name: When we have a costs with 6% and 8% and a project budget 500 and a revenue potential 250, we expect that project has a breakeven 581.3953488250
When we have a costs with 10% and 15% and a project budget 10000 and a revenue potential 500, we expect that project has a breakeven 13333.3333333500
When we have provider with 1000 advance and 500 settlement, we expect that project has a tramaFee: 75.0000000000
When we have provider with 500 advance and 250 settlement, we expect that project has a tramaFee: 37.5000000000
